body_html:
Thanks for the information and report.
Unfortunately, we don't have the bandwidth to maintain FreeBSD support at this time (the list of supported platforms is at https://www.tensorflow.org/install/)

That said, we're more than happy to accept pull requests that can improve compatibility on other platforms. Marking as "Contributions Welcome" to address that.

body:
Thanks for the information and report.
Unfortunately, we don't have the bandwidth to maintain FreeBSD support at this time (the list of supported platforms is at https://www.tensorflow.org/install/)

That said, we're more than happy to accept pull requests that can improve compatibility on other platforms. Marking as "Contributions Welcome" to address that.
